  "prompt": "Which is the best phone under 16k INR?",
  "response": "As of the latest updates, several good smartphones are available under \u20b916,000 INR in India. The \"best\" phone can depend on individual preferences regarding features like camera quality, battery life, display, performance, and brand loyalty. Here are some popular options:\n\n1. **Realme Narzo 50**:\n   - Processor: MediaTek Helio G96\n   - Display: 6.6-inch Full HD+ LCD\n   - Camera: 50MP primary camera\n   - Battery: 5000mAh with 33W fast charging\n\n2. **Redmi Note 10**:\n   - Processor: Qualcomm Snapdragon 678\n   - Display: 6.43-inch AMOLED Full HD+\n   - Camera: 48MP quad-camera setup\n   - Battery: 5000mAh with 33W fast charging\n\n3. **Samsung Galaxy M32**:\n   - Processor: MediaTek Helio G80\n   - Display: 6.4-inch Super AMOLED, 90Hz refresh rate\n   - Camera: 64MP quad-camera setup\n   - Battery: 6000mAh\n\n4. **Poco M3 Pro 5G**:\n   - Processor: MediaTek Dimensity 700\n   - Display: 6.5-inch Full HD+ LCD, 90Hz refresh rate\n   - Camera: 48MP triple-camera setup\n   - Battery: 5000mAh\n\n5. **Motorola Moto G60**:\n   - Processor: Qualcomm Snapdragon 732G\n   - Display: 6.8-inch Full HD+ LCD, 120Hz refresh rate\n   - Camera: 108MP triple-camera setup\n   - Battery: 6000mAh\n\nThese options offer good performance and features for their price range. You should consider what aspects are most important to you, whether it's battery life, camera quality, display type, or performance specs, and choose accordingly.",
